<p>TJs letter of uncertain date acknowledged by Fleming is missing. For the balloting on officers for the six troops of horse, see <span class="ref-st" title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ &lt;i&gt;Proceedings&lt;/i&gt; of &lt;i&gt;the Convention of Delegates&lt;/i&gt; &lt;i&gt;in the Colony of Virginia&lt;/i&gt; (cited by session and date of publication) ]"><span class="hi-italic" style="font-style: italic;">Conv. Jour.</span></span>, May 1776, 1816 edn., p. 458, where the names of the candidates are given in their full and correct forms.</p></div>
